118
00:06:52.736 --> 00:06:56.376
And so in addition to trying to introduce, let's say,

119
00:06:56.436 --> 00:07:00.356
dendritic cells and activate them with STING agonists and so on,

120
00:07:01.416 --> 00:07:04.056
maybe it's going to be necessary to

121
00:07:05.395 --> 00:07:08.716
change the phenotype or change the differentiation state of the

