00:07:16.656 --> 00:07:20.536
what is present in non-T cell inflamed tumors, obviously, you have tumor cells,

125
00:07:20.636 --> 00:07:20.856
you have

126
00:07:21.716 --> 00:07:24.896
the vasculature, the neovasculature, you have fibroblasts, and you have

127
00:07:24.936 --> 00:07:26.896
macrophages. You always have macrophages.

128
00:07:27.176 --> 00:07:28.756
It's just that the macrophages are different.

129
00:07:29.796 --> 00:07:33.156
So, through our work over the past several

130
00:07:33.256 --> 00:07:36.676
years, looking at different dimensions of

