00:08:52.656 --> 00:08:56.496
went on to respond, and other bacterial entities enriched in

153
00:08:56.576 --> 00:08:58.256
patients who did not respond.

154
00:08:59.956 --> 00:09:03.936
I'll show in a minute how we think that this is causal in about

155
00:09:03.956 --> 00:09:04.936
half of the patients.

156
00:09:05.816 --> 00:09:09.485
And both of these are important. I won't show the data, but we think there are

