00:09:09.516 --> 00:09:12.956
immune-supportive bacteria, and then there are bacteria, we put them in, and we

158
00:09:12.976 --> 00:09:14.816
lose the immune response against the tumor.

159
00:09:16.016 --> 00:09:19.335
And obviously, Jen Margol's group and Laurent Siefogels group

160
00:09:20.196 --> 00:09:23.876
found similar observations. Although the details of the bacteria aren't

