00:09:39.296 --> 00:09:42.596
And the way we were studying functionality was by

167
00:09:42.656 --> 00:09:43.306
transferring

168
00:09:44.216 --> 00:09:47.716
a sample from a patient into germ-free mice that didn't have their own microbiome

