00:09:54.336 --> 00:09:58.216
studies that we want to do, tracking the cancer immunity cycle and

172
00:09:58.756 --> 00:10:01.056
doing single-cell RNA-seq and so on.

173
00:10:01.096 --> 00:10:03.156
You can't just do that with one set of mice.

174
00:10:03.216 --> 00:10:04.556
We needed a stable,

175
00:10:06.436 --> 00:10:08.776
let's say, colony of mice. So what we decided to do

