00:11:22.736 --> 00:11:26.696
is once we had these sets of mice and we were mapping

198
00:11:26.796 --> 00:11:30.126
out where's the defect in the immune response in the mice that

199
00:11:30.236 --> 00:11:33.966
have the non-supportive microbiota from a

