00:49:09.422 --> 00:49:12.262
We're certainly not the first one to observe this, but the

841
00:49:12.802 --> 00:49:14.062
immunologists among you

842
00:49:14.942 --> 00:49:18.222
will be aware that those clusters are

843
00:49:18.702 --> 00:49:22.382
commonly seen on flow cytometry plots, but they're typically gated out

844
00:49:22.882 --> 00:49:24.202
