849
00:49:40.522 --> 00:49:44.422
They're tumor reactive, they produce more cytokines, the TCRs are clonally expanded

850
00:49:44.461 --> 00:49:46.462
and are much better killers in vitro and in vivo.

851
00:49:47.342 --> 00:49:51.002
So what we're interested to do now is to use this

